title: Fat is not the enemy and green beauty
description:
Not only do you have to be concerned about what you put "in" your body, you have to be concerned about "what" you put on your body.  Paige Padgett joins Jillian to talk some Green Beauty Tips. Jillian takes caller questions on diet, fitness, nutrition, inspiration and overall wellness.
